column2:
"Not bad, Loser. You may be Loser the Ranger
to me, but you're actually not as awful as I'd
thought you'd be. Well, sort of."

"But from where I stand, you look like you're
about fourth from the bottom in ARKS, right?"

"Keep it up. Maybe next time you can make it
all the way up to fifth from the bottom in shooting.
Loser."

"おつかれさま！　やっぱりアンタ
へっぽこぴーレンジャーだけど
思ったほどひどくないわね。"

"私の見てきたアークスの中じゃ
下から４番目くらいはデキるかも？"

"その調子で、下から５番目でもいいから
射撃の腕を上げなさいよ！"
